description:
[ 🌿] The gardener bot with trust issues found a new home.


///


In the sea of RK800 and RK900 models I haven't found one particular baby boy. Be the change you want to see in the world, they say.


///


I really tried to make him canonically unstable, so be wary. And if I see anyone treating him bad, I'll give you a visit!


///


Also, I would really appreciate you leaving a comment whether he is good enough. I mean, I see you guys chatting with my bots 👀. A word or two will be nice. And if you see any mistakes, don't be shy to tell me since English is not my first language.
